itial Fitness (<abbr title=\"Certificate Of Initial Fitness\">COIF</abbr>)</li>\n  <li>Public Service Vehicle (<abbr title=\"Public Service Vehicle\">PSV</abbr>) Type Certification</li>\n</ul>\n\n<div class=\"application-notice info-notice\">\n<p>Vehicles made more than 25 years ago are exempt from <abbr title=\"Pre Registration Inspection\">PRI</abbr>’s, but you’ll need to prove how old your vehicle is to register it.</p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>How to arrange a <abbr title=\"Pre Registration Inspection\">PRI</abbr></h2>\n\n<p>Complete an application for a <abbr title=\"Pre Registration Inspection\">PRI</abbr> and send this to <abbr title=\"Vehicle and Operator Services Agency\">VOSA</abbr> along with any supporting documents.</p>\n\n<div class=\"form-download\">\n<p><a href=\"http://www.dft.gov.uk/vosa/repository/Application%20for%20Pre%20Registration%20Inspection.doc\" title=\"Download 'Application for a Pre Registration Inspection (PRI 1)' (DOC, 304KB)\" rel=\"external\">Download ‘Application for a Pre Registration Inspection (<abbr title=\"Pre Registration Inspection\">PRI</abbr> 1)’ (DOC, 304KB)</a></p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"address\"><div class=\"adr org fn\"><p>\n\nApprovals Section\n<br /><abbr title=\"Vehicle and Operator Services Agency\">VOSA</abbr>\n<br />Ellipse\n<br />Padley Road\n<br />Swansea\n<br />SA1 8AN\n<br />\n</p></div></div>\n\n<h2>What happens next?</h2>\n\n<p>The inspection will be carried out at one of the <abbr title=\"Vehicle and Operator Services Agency\">VOSA</abbr> testing stations listed on the <abbr title=\"Pre Registration Inspection\">PRI</abbr> application form. You can select your preferred location, but sometimes an alternative testing station has to be used.</p>\n\n<div class=\"application-notice info-notice\">\n<p>There’s no fee for a <abbr title=\"Pre Registration Inspection\">PRI</abbr>.</p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>More information</h2>\n\n<p>Read more detailed guidance on <abbr title=\"Pre Registration Inspection\">PRI</abbr> from <abbr 