ant the test. </p>\n\n<div class=\"form-download\">\n<p><a href=\"http://www.businesslink.gov.uk/Transport_Theme_files/067020_Application_for_TIR_GV_62_0810.pdf\" title=\"Download 'Application for TIR test' form (PDF, 43KB)\" rel=\"external\">Download ‘Application for <abbr title=\"Transports Internationaux Routiers\">TIR</abbr> test’ (PDF, 43KB)</a></p>\n</div>\n\n<p>You need to fill in a separate form for each vehicle or trailer.</p>\n\n<p>Send your application and a cheque (made payable to &lsquo;<abbr title=\"Vehicle and Operator Services Agency\">VOSA</abbr>&rsquo;) to the test station where you want the vehicle tested.</p>\n\n<p>You can find details of <a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://www.transportoffice.gov.uk/crt/doitonline/bl/vosateststationlocations/vosateststationlocations.htm\" title=\"VOSA Test Station locations\"><abbr title=\"Vehicle and Operator Services Agency\">VOSA</abbr> Test Station locations</a> on the <abbr title=\"Vehicle and Operator Services Agency\">VOSA</abbr> website or contact the <abbr title=\"Vehicle and Operator Services Agency\">VOSA</abbr> Helpline.</p>\n\n<div class=\"contact\">\n<p><strong><abbr title=\"Vehicle and Operator Services Agency\">VOSA</abbr> Helpline</strong><br />\n0300 123 9000</p>\n</div>\n\n<h3>Cancelling a test</h3>\n\n<p>You&rsquo;ll need to give adequate notice (normally 3 days) to cancel an inspection. Otherwise the fee won&rsquo;t be refunded. </p>\n\n<h2><abbr title=\"Transports Internationaux Routiers\">TIR</abbr> test fees</h2>\n\n<table>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Initial inspection</td>\n      <td>£106</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Re-inspection</td>\n      <td>£70</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Type approval</td>\n      <td>£644</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Type variation</td>\n      <td>£106</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Certificate of conformity</td>\n      <td>£14</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Duplicate certificate</td>\n      <td>£14</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbod