g":"single-vehicle-approval","order":6,"title":"Single Vehicle Approval","body":"<h2>Who can use the scheme?</h2>\n\n<p>The <a href=\"/vehicle-approval/individual-vehicle-approval\" title=\"Individual Vehicle Approval (IVA) scheme\">Individual Vehicle Approval (<abbr title=\"Individual Vehicle Approval\">IVA</abbr>) scheme</a> is replacing the Single Vehicle Approval (<abbr title=\"Single Vehicle Approval\">SVA</abbr>) scheme. From now on, you can use the <abbr title=\"Individual Vehicle Approval\">IVA</abbr> scheme for any type of vehicle needing type approval except for special purpose light goods vehicles.</p>\n\n<p>Until 29 October 2014, you can still use the <abbr title=\"Single Vehicle Approval\">SVA</abbr> scheme for special purpose light goods vehicles not more than 3,500kg gross vehicle weight that need first licensing and registration in the UK and are less than 10 years old.</p>\n\n<div class=\"form-download\">\n<p><a href=\"http://www.dft.gov.uk/vosa/repository/SVA%20to%20IVA%20v2.0%20APRIL%202012.pdf\" title=\"Download 'Guide to the differences between SVA and IVA for light goods vehicles' (PDF, 294KB)\" rel=\"external\">Download ‘Guide to the differences between <abbr title=\"Single Vehicle Approval\">SVA</abbr> and <abbr title=\"Individual Vehicle Approval\">IVA</abbr> for light goods vehicles’ (PDF, 294KB)</a></p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Application form</h2>\n\n<p>Send your completed application to the address on the form along with any relevant documents.</p>\n\n<div class=\"form-download\">\n<p><a href=\"http://www.dft.gov.uk/vosa/repository/Application%20for%20Ministers%20Approval%20Certificate%20for%20Vehicles%20(SVA%201).doc\" title=\"Download SVA application form (DOC, 696KB)\" rel=\"external\">Download ‘<abbr title=\"Single Vehicle Approval\">SVA</abbr> application form’ (DOC, 696KB)</a>\n<a href=\"http://www.dft.gov.uk/vosa/repository/SVA%201%20Guidance%20Notes.pdf\" title=\"Download 'Guidance on completing SVA application form' (PDF, 135KB)\" rel=\"